!> @brief   read coordinate data from CHARMM CRD file
!! @authors Yuji Sugita (YS), Jaewoon Jung (JJ), Takaharu Mori (TM), 
!!          Kenta YAMADA (KYMD), Kiyoshi Yagi (KY)
